service notes: Title: Successful Camshaft Position Sensor Replacement in 2022 Hyundai Tucson

Issue:
- P0342 code (Camshaft Position Sensor Circuit Low Input Bank 1)
- Extended engine startup time
- Low voltage on Camshaft Position Sensor signal circuit
- Second occurrence since April 2025

Diagnostic Steps:
1. Scanned and confirmed P0342 code
2. Verified low voltage on signal circuit
3. Checked service history revealing previous sensor replacement

Repair Solution:
1. Replaced Bank 1 Camshaft Position Sensor
2. Installed Bosch replacement part (P/N: 393503E110)
3. Performed post-repair verification

Final Results:
- Engine running normally
- Check engine light cleared and remains off
- Starting time returned to normal
- Smooth engine operation confirmed
- All systems functioning as expected

Technical Notes:
- Second sensor replacement in short timeframe
- Recommend monitoring for:
  * Wiring harness integrity
  * Voltage stability
  * Any signs of electrical interference
- Consider full circuit inspection if issue recurs

